<use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104biz1665702659147.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/biz1665702659147.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/biz1665702659147.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"biz1665702659147\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set a user-defined archive file version and description that can be displayed by other\n    utilities.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"biz1665702659147__topic_d176900e1_d176901e1_d176902e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"biz1665702659147__p_d176903e1_d176904e1_d176905e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">urm</span> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Switches</var>} <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">info</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ArchiveFile</var> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">+</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ArchiveFile</var>} {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Options</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"biz1665702659147__section_vgs_kr1_dcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d949439e78\">Switches</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">See <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fpl1665702658861.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fpl1665702658861.html\" title=\"Executable for the Uniface Resource Manager, a command line utility for creating and manipulating Uniface archive files and other resources, files and DBMS tables.\">urm</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"biz1665702659147__section_xl5_mr1_dcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d949439e94\">Parameters</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"biz1665702659147__ul_x52_4r1_dcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"biz1665702659147__li_d54020e1_d54021e1_d54022e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">ArchiveFile</var>—name of an archive\n               file, including path and extension</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"biz1665702659147__li_d54023e1_d54024e1_d54025e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Options</var>—additional parameters\n               to control what is listed or validated.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"biz1665702659147__table_d18644e1_d18645e1_d18646e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Options for <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">urm info</span></span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"biz1665702659147__table_d18644e1_d18645e1_d18646e1__entry__1\">Option</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"biz1665702659147__table_d18644e1_d18645e1_d18646e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"biz1665702659147__table_d18644e1_d18645e1_d18646e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-description</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"biz1665702659147__table_d18644e1_d18645e1_d18646e1__entry__2\">Set the description of the archive file. If\n                        there is already a description, it is overwritten.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"biz1665702659147__table_d18644e1_d18645e1_d18646e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-version</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"biz1665702659147__table_d18644e1_d18645e1_d18646e1__entry__2\">Set the version for the archive file. The\n                        version property can only be written once. It cannot be overwritten.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"biz1665702659147__section_hjm_qr1_dcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d949439e165\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">A Uniface archive file (UAR) holds an information record that contains the following\n            information:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"biz1665702659147__ul_pkz_sr1_dcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"biz1665702659147__li_d54026e1_d54027e1_d54028e1\">Name of the archive file</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"biz1665702659147__li_d54029e1_d54030e1_d54031e1\">Version of Uniface used to create the UAR</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"biz1665702659147__li_d54032e1_d54033e1_d54034e1\">Creation date</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"biz1665702659147__li_d54035e1_d54036e1_d54037e1\">UAR version</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"biz1665702659147__li_d54038e1_d54039e1_d54040e1\">Description</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"biz1665702659147__p_d176927e1_d176928e1_d176929e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">urm info</span> to set the\n            values of the last two properties.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"biz1665702659147__note_w5757ab1b5b5_w5758ab1b5_w5759ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> You can only use this function\n            once. The properties cannot be set separately. For example, if you set the version but\n            not the description, it is not possible to add the description later.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"biz1665702659147__p_d176930e1_d176931e1_d176932e1\">The information can be displayed by the\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/who</span> command line switch or the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">urm show</span>\n            command.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"biz1665702659147__section_vvh_vr1_dcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d949439e211\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">urm info</span></h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"biz1665702659147__p_d176936e1_d176937e1_d176938e1\">The following example shows that an existing\n            description is overwritten:</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"biz1665702659147__section_gjh_qs1_dcc\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"biz1665702659147__pre_fxd_wks_gxb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">urm info C:/u10/myarchive.uar -description=\"Adapted by MyCorp for YourCorp.\" –version=\"A10.1.4\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"biz1665702659147__p_d176939e1_d176940e1_d176941e1\">Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">urm show</span> displays the\n            information as:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre screen language-plaintext\" id=\"biz1665702659147__pre_gxd_wks_gxb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">Archive (myarchive) created with : 10.1.01.00 ( 0806)\nArchive (myarchive) creation date : 28 Aug 2014 14:16:00\nArchive (myarchive) description : Adapted by MyCorp for YourCorp.\nArchive (myarchive) version : A10.1.4</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cwn1665702659361.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>urm show</a><p>Show the version record, readme file, or contents of one or more archive files, or validate the contents.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wsn1665702659009.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/who</a><p>Display the information about the Uniface configuration.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526073\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526073\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "urm info Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Set a user-defined archive file version and description that can be displayed by other utilities. urm { Switches } info ArchiveFile { + ArchiveFile } { Options } Switches See urm . Parameters ArchiveFile —name of an archive file, including path and extension Options —additional parameters to control what is listed or validated. Table 1. Options for urm info Option Description -description Set the description of the archive file. If there is already a description, it is overwritten. -version Set the version for the archive file. The version property can only be written once. It cannot be overwritten. Description A Uniface archive file (UAR) holds an information record that contains the following information: Name of the archive file Version of Uniface used to create the UAR Creation date UAR version Description You can use urm info to set the values of the last two properties. Note: You can only use this function once. The properties cannot be set separately. For example, if you set the version but not the description, it is not possible to add the description later. The information can be displayed by the /who command line switch or the urm show command. Example: Using urm info The following example shows that an existing description is overwritten: urm info C:/u10/myarchive.uar -description=\"Adapted by MyCorp for YourCorp.\" –version=\"A10.1.4\" Copy Using urm show displays the information as: Archive (myarchive) created with : 10.1.01.00 ( 0806) Archive (myarchive) creation date : 28 Aug 2014 14:16:00 Archive (myarchive) description : Adapted by MyCorp for YourCorp. Archive (myarchive) version : A10.1.4 Copy Related Links urm show Show the version record, readme file, or contents of one or more archive files, or validate the contents. /who Display the information about the Uniface configuration. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}